swp_compiler_ss13.fuc.parser.grammar

Class Production

  • java.lang.Object
    • swp_compiler_ss13.fuc.parser.grammar.Production

  • public final class Production
extends java.lang.Object
    A production consists of a left hand side NonTerminal and a list of right hand side Symbols. If there are productions with more than one right hand sides (in parser books separated by "|"), each of these sides must be represented by its own Production instance.
